title: How.Evolution.Is.Scientific.DVD.iso
description:
This is a DVD disc of my 6-part YouTube series, "How Evolution Is Scientific," on the scientific basis for evolution, refuting lies from creationists.

This DVD contains full NTSC-resolution versions of all six videos, and includes English subtitles. It also includes other freely-available videos referenced in the series, including three from cdk007, a video I made about Piltdown Man, and the clip of students doing a rather stupid protest of evolution.

There is also a Blu-Ray version here: http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/4797489
